*   Are you using BibTeX?  If so, what bibliography style are you using (e.g., `plain`, `unsrt`, `abbrv`)?
*   How many authors do you have?
*   What is the complexity of the information you want to include in the footnotes? (e.g., just brief notes, email addresses, affiliations, complex statements)
